<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<!--<h4>Side-1.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śārvari saṁvatsara Ā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śvija śu 15 gu śrī
<lb n="3" break="no"/>manmahāmaṁḍalē
<lb n="4" break="no"/>śvarulaina śrī vodāḍi
<lb n="5"/>rājyādhipatulaina
<lb n="6"/>śrīpratāpavallabha
</p>

<!--<h4>Side-2.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="7"/>rājumahāpau
<lb n="8" break="no"/>tṛluṁgāriki nija
<lb n="9" break="no"/>hitulaina valla
<lb n="10" break="no"/>yapadālu mahā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>pautṛluṁgārunnu
<lb n="12"/>maku putrapautrabhi 
</p>

<!--<h4>Side-3.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="13" break="no"/>vṛddhigānu Anavara
<lb n="14" break="no"/>pugrāmamu śrīju
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ttaḍa vallabharāya
<lb n="16"/>luku peṭabhāgāna
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ku yistimi yigrā
<lb n="18" break="no"/>mānaku yavvarugāni ta
</p>

<!--<h4>Side-4.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="19" break="no"/>ppinanu tava śvāhastana
<lb n="20" break="no"/>gohattebraṁhmaha
<lb n="21" break="no"/>tte pātakālu ceśe
<lb n="22" break="no"/>na pāpānaṁboduru va
<lb n="23" break="no"/>llabharāyala Amṛta
<lb n="24" break="no"/>maṇilōnu viṣamu pe
<lb n="25" break="no"/>ṭina dōṣāna bōduru śrī
</p>

<!--<h4>Side-5.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="26"/>śrīpādālu mahāpātṛlū gaṁ
<lb n="27" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> peṭina Aḍḍanu Evaḍu peṭlaḍu vā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="28"/>ḍu vurivāri mōḍatāgināḍu Ā
<lb n="29" break="no"/>ḍadi Ayina gāḍidamōḍa tāhu
<lb n="30"/>nu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
</p>

